<p class="title">Chapter 10: Notes on a Lovable Adventurer (0) (No.10)</p>
<p class="para"><i>Where did you meet Dad?</i>
<br>Hmm... I forget.</p>
<p class="para"><i>You're kidding.</i>
<br>Heh. I'll let you read my diary once you're older.
<br>It's all in there.</p>
<p class="para">
<i>But I want to read it NOW!</i>
<br>We all want things, kiddo.</p>
<p class="para"><i>Okay, fine. Why did you marry Dad?</i>
